Two new superpowers on top of the existing retention engine:

Revenue-at-risk (pure client-side): roRisk() turns each customer's
lifecycle stage + personal cadence + logged outcomes into a churn
probability and a ৳-at-risk figure. The follow-up list now sorts by
money bleeding out today (within priority tier), cards show a risk
pill, and the mission dashboard shows total ৳ slipping away. De-risks
customers who just booked; escalates complaints and dormant win-backs.

AI copilot: new Supabase edge function `ai-copilot` (OpenAI) drafts a
personal, on-brand WhatsApp message from the customer's real history.
A ✨ AI button on every card opens an editable draft sheet with Redraft
and Send-on-WhatsApp. Falls back to the proven templates when the
function is missing, errors, or the device is offline — never a dead end.

Verified: inline scripts parse clean, roRisk unit-tested across
scenarios, page boots with no JS errors, AI overlay + risk pill render.

